<view class="page-shell membership-page">
  <view class="membership-hero card">
    <view class="membership-badge">唯一套餐</view>
    <view class="membership-title">{{planName}}</view>
    <view class="membership-price">{{priceText}}</view>
    <view class="membership-copy">
      你前面已经明确只做年会员，所以这里先把套餐结构彻底收敛。后面接微信支付时，我们只保留这一条购买链路。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="benefit-card card">
    <view class="section-title">会员权益</view>
    <view class="section-subtitle">现在先把权益文案和支付入口占住</view>

    <view class="benefit-list">
      <view wx:for="{{benefits}}" wx:key="index" class="benefit-item">
        <view class="benefit-dot"></view>
        <view class="benefit-text">{{item}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="purchase-card card">
    <view class="purchase-title">支付接入说明</view>
    <view class="purchase-text">
      下一步会把这里接到微信支付下单接口，再由小程序端调用 wx.requestPayment 完成购买。
    </view>
    <button class="button-primary" bindtap="handlePurchase">预留支付按钮</button>
  </view>
</view>
